[Back to Top]



A career in ComfortDelGro will open your horizons to one of the world's largest land transport groups.




With a staff strength and fleet size of more than 22,000 and more than 44,700 respectively, ComfortDelGro is a multi-billion-dollar international group that is well on its way to achieving its vision of becoming the world's land transport operator of choice. If you have what it takes to bring ComfortDelGro to even greater heights, we welcome you to join us in our global endeavours.
 
ComfortDelGro Corporation Limited
Our Singapore subsidiaries:


ComfortDelGro Bus Pte Ltd

ComfortDelGro Driving Centre Pte Ltd

ComfortDelGro Engineering Pte Ltd

ComfortDelGro Rent-A-Car Pte Ltd

Comfort Transportation Pte Ltd / CityCab Pte Ltd

Moove Media Pte Ltd

SBS Transit Ltd

Setsco Services Pte Ltd

VICOM Ltd


Our China subsidiaries:


